query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 10 AND q.view_count <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('akka-stream',
'andengine',
'arangodb',
'c#-3.0',
'calculated-columns',
'cx-freeze',
'delimiter',
'explode',
'gdi',
'google-colaboratory',
'jna',
'karma-runner',
'perl6',
'viewport',
'yesod');
